metadata.name: Pepepunk Eggs
metadata.description: Introducing the Pepepunks NFT reveal! As a special bonus to all our early adopters, we're giving you a frog egg NFT. This egg represents the birth of your very own unique Pepepunk, waiting to hatch and come to life. It's a symbol of the exciting journey you're about to embark on as a member of the Pepepunks community. The egg is a rare and valuable collectible in its own right, and its hatching will be a moment to remember. Keep your frog egg NFT close and watch as your Pepepunk takes shape and comes to life. Don't miss out on this exclusive opportunity to own a piece of digital meme history
